    Description
    AutoScore
    This command will: Open the gripper Drive backwards the specified distance Get ready for pickup of another piece (close grip, lower arm, open grip) Rotate 180 degrees Note: This class assume the robot and arm are already positioned to score!
    PickupFromGround
    This command will: Close the gripper Drive backwards the specified distance (to prevent a stuck arm) Raise the arm a safe driving position Note: This class assume the robot and arm are already positioned to to pickup a piece!
    PrepareForGroundPickup
    This command will: Move the arm all the way down Open the gripper
